*Technical Notes*
The Seasonal Specials module ({{app/spaces/seasonal-specials/modules/main/guards/LoggedInUserGuard.tsx}}) has a similar authentication guard. that can be adapted for Good Chop's needs. 

The guard for /one-time-deliveriesshould redirect to /login, example

{noformat}      const loginUrl = `/login?redirect=${encodeURIComponent(redirectUrl)}`;
      replace(loginUrl);{noformat}

The good-chop guard should redirect non-logged-in users to the login page with current path preserved

Testing Considerations

# Verify redirect behavior for non-authenticated users
# Verify authenticated users can access protected content
# Verify redirect URL is properly encoded and preserved
{panel}

